---
title: Cali-Style Turkey Cheeseburgers with Guacamole and Potato Coins
description: Surf's up at the dinner table tonight with these California-inspired burgers! Classic guacamole and melty cheese pair beautifully with tender turkey.  Don't forget to dunk those golden potato coins in the guac, too!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/burgers-au-fromage-et-a-la-dinde-style-californien-92d86f1c.jpg
